===Etymology 1===
From alteration of dialectal ''simper'', from {{inh|en|enm|simperen||to simmer}}, of possibly imitative origin. First attested in the intransitive sense. The noun is from the verb. {{etydate|late 15<sup>th</sup> century}}.

